<!-- fwtable fwsrc="未命名" fwbase="sr.jpg" fwstyle="Dreamweaver" fwdocid = "1344182167" fwnested="1" -->
  <tr><!-- row 1 -->
    <td align="right" valign="top">
    
		<!--标题开始-->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:18pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	《抱朴子外篇&#xB7;嘉遁》的道教思想
	      </div>
	      <!-- 副标题 -->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:16pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	
	      </div>
	      <!--标题结束-->
		<div style="text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>
		<img name="sr_r3_c1" src="images/sr_r3_c1.gif" width="293" height="32" border="0" id="sr_r3_c1" alt="" /></div>
		<!--图片-->
		
		<!--图片结束-->
		<!-- 作者 -->
		
			<div style="font-family:'宋体'; font-size:12pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center;padding-bottom:8px;">
		      	
		    </div>
		
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 显示内容 -->
	   		<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">宋</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;晶&nbsp;&nbsp;杨铭顺</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">葛洪是东晋时期一位卓有建树的道教神学理论家，所著《抱朴子》一书，由《内篇》二十卷和《外篇》五十卷组成，是晋以前道教理论和方术集大成的一部恢弘巨制。学者们对于葛洪道教思想的研究多着重于《内篇》。依葛洪自叙：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">其内篇言神仙方药、鬼怪变化、养生延年、禳邪却祸之事，属道家；其外篇言人间得失，世事臧否，属儒家</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">①</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">宋尤袤《遂初堂书目》始将内外篇合二而一，归入道家类。清《四库全书总目提要》子部道家类尤而效之，据明卢舜治本著录，题曰《抱朴子》内外篇八卷。并谓《外篇》大旨</font><font face="Times New Roman">&lsquo;</font><font face="宋体">亦以黄、老为宗</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rsquo;&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">②</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">那么，作为道教理论家，葛洪的《抱朴子外篇》在应用儒家思想议论人间得失的同时是否涉及道家道教思想呢？目前这方面的研究还相对比较薄弱。事实上，《外篇》蕴藏着丰富的道教思想，是研究汉晋道教思想的重要参考资料，值得认真挖掘、研究。本文仅从葛洪的作品《抱朴子外篇<font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font><font face="宋体">嘉遁》着手，浅析其道教思想。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《嘉遁》是《外篇》的首篇，题目本身指恰到好处的隐遁，潜含待机而动之义。在葛洪的时代，儒者与道士的思想矛盾比较突出，葛洪作为兼儒道两有的大思想家，他运用《嘉遁》中怀冰先生和赴势公子主客对话的形式，假借怀冰先生之口，以入仕还是隐遁为核心话题，从道教信徒的立场出发，表达出了寡欲不争、虚淡静寂、贵己重生、弘道养正、藏光守朴、逍遥隐遁的道教思想，从而在理论上充分阐述了道教隐逸遁世的思想。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一、寡欲不争，虚淡静寂</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">从《嘉遁》开篇对怀冰先生的描述来看，怀冰先生十分鄙视那些栖栖遑遑、周流游说仁政礼治的人，对一些所谓的古圣先贤终日<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">吐哺</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">、</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">握发</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">的烦劳，寄予了悲叹。他让出肥田沃土、物产丰盈之地，自自然然地躬耕于</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">斥卤</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，具有不争之品格。怀冰先生平素还</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">背朝华于朱门，保恬寂乎蓬户</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">谓荣显为不幸，以玉帛为草土</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">③</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">是一位不慕爵禄，反视荣华显赫为不幸，将玉帛当粪土的寡欲虚寂之隐仕。其不争之心、不争之行，恰如怀冰先生操行冰霜、清雅高洁之名。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">怀冰先生超凡离俗的品质，具有道教徒向往的至人特征。<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">至人无为，栖神冲漠，不役志于禄利</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">④</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">是葛洪对至人的理解，与庄子<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">是故至人无为，大圣不作，观于天地之谓也</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑤</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">的思想一脉相承。至人是不着力于功名利禄，能够领悟大道、效法天地、无为顺物的高尚之士。葛洪列举了夏朝以来能做到去名去功、有至人无己精神的至人，如<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">巢栖之客</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">许由，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">尧以天下让许由，许由不受，退而耕于颍水之阳，终身不见</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">；</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑥</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">握耒之贤</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">柏成子高，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">柏成操耜，而不屑诸侯之高</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑦</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">他们都是以寡欲虚寂之心对待富贵名利，不为物累，自然<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">害辱不能加也</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。葛洪还列举了历史上的关龙逢、比干，都因忠德进谏反获大刑，韩信、黥布因功高盖主反遭击杀，因为他们</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">躇峙于险途</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，故有</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">倾坠</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">之患。葛洪明白</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">以欲广则浊和，故委世务而不纡晒；以位极者忧深，故背势利而无余疑</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑧</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">禄厚者责重，爵尊者神劳</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑨</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">的道理，他想告诫人们应当寡欲不争，淡泊名利。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">寡欲的反面是贪欲，贪欲让人做起事来瞻前顾后、畏首畏尾、忧虑深重。道教提倡寡欲不争，并不是要灭掉人的正当欲望，而是提倡减少人的贪欲，反对过分的放纵、好胜、竞贪之心。世间的名位足以引起人的争逐，财富足以激起人的贪念，那么，评判人生价值的标准何在呢？不是官爵的高低，也不是财产的多寡，<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">安贫者以无财为富，甘卑者以不仕为荣</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑩</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">贵不以爵也，富不以财也</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span>11</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">所以，不必伸长脖颈费力地去争夺尊贵的名贤、俸禄的高低。<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">一枝足以戢鸾羽，何烦乎丰林？潢洿足以泛龙鳞，岂事乎沧海？</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span>12</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">那些汲汲企求名禄者，<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">亢悔而贪荣之欲不灭，忌毁辱而争肆之情不遣</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>13</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">都是<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">昧乎可欲</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，为欲望所蒙蔽，这正是忘记了老子《道德经》的</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">少私寡欲</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>14</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">祸莫大于不知足，咎莫大于欲得</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span>15</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">的告诫。所以，葛洪强调<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">贪进不虑负乘之祸，受任不计不堪之败</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，光贪图前进却不考虑居非其位，才不称职，会招致祸患，入仕为官却不计较不能胜任引起的败亡恶果，这样的行为十分危险。甚至有些急功近利者，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">集不择木，仕不料世</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，葛洪形容为</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">伺河龙之睡而拨明珠，居量表之宠而冀无患</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，必然是</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">耽漏刻之安，蔽必至之危</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span>16</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">的结局。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">如何做到寡欲不争，绝尽贪欲之心呢？道教是主张虚淡静寂，清贫柔弱的。怀冰先生在回答赴势公子时的表情就十分地耐人寻味，他<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">萧然遐眺，游气天卫，情神辽缅，旁若无物</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，完全一幅虚淡静寂的神态。葛洪倡导</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">躬耕以食之，穿井以饮之，短褐以蔽之，蓬庐以覆之，弹咏以娱之，呼吸以延之</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>17</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">不萦翮于腐鼠</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">不改乐于箪瓢</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，要学儒者颜回的品格，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">一箪食，一瓢饮，在陋巷</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，却</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">弱于受谏，怵于待禄</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，安贫甘卑，虚淡静寂。如果说葛洪年轻时有救世思想，然这种思想也有其复杂的一面，至少其中也蕴含着道教修炼者的追求：虚静寂寞、清静无为、绝思去欲、澄心静虑。事实上，葛洪本人便为人淡泊寡欲，不好荣利，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">子弟躬耕，以典籍自娱</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，他一生特别提倡高尚的道教精神修炼，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">绝弃世务，则曷缘</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。因为修习玄静会使心灵处于虚寂纯净的状态，此时超验的道自然会朝人的精神世界呈现。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">二、贵己重生，弘道养正</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">葛洪在《嘉遁》举出<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">杨朱吝其一毛</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">值得注意。在他的时代，杨朱学派是有影响力的一派，其基本观点是贵己重生。据许地山先生《道教史》的说法，杨朱也是老子的道家学派之一。渊源于先秦道家的贵己重生，后来成为了道教教理之一。杨朱不为天下之大利而拔一胫毛，并不是极端的利己主义，他只不过要保住一个不受增损的自我而已。贵己是相对于贵名利而言的，与《道德经》的</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">名与身孰亲</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">的观点一致，因为杨朱轻物重生，贵己而不贵爵禄，不拿生命作交易换取田宅爵禄。葛洪曾深叹：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">身名并全者甚稀！</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span>18</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">对于<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">名</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，应当不争爵禄，放下争名，淡泊虚寂待之。对于</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">身</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，要如何去保全呢？</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">首先，葛洪主张<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">守常待终</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span>19</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《列子》有<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">处常得终</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">的说法。《道德经》对</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">常</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">给予了定位，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">常</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">本身是道教中教理教义的名词，指万物运动与变化中不变之律则，与道相通。老子说</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">复命曰常，知常曰明。不知常，妄作凶</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span>20</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">复归是万物经过了自己的生命显示后向自己的根源处去报到，复归于人的本性就是<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">常</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，了解了</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">常</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">叫做</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">明</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，不了解</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">常</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，轻举妄动就会出乱子。老子复归的思想对葛洪是有影响的。守常就是让人心原本的清明透彻得以保持，但往往智巧会使人心受到蒙蔽，所以，葛洪的修道方法之一是主张</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">遣智慧以绝俗</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。修道者要以恬养知，即以恬淡的性情养知，无须凭借智慧行事，不因知识和智巧而扰乱恬淡之性，不须刻意用智，要舍弃智巧，复归于原本清净透明的境地，这样才能守常待终。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">其次，葛洪倡导<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">不可受全而归残</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span>21</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">重视生命完全的观念在儒家也十分流行。《礼记<font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font><font face="宋体">祭义》有：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">天之所生，地之所养，无人为大。父母全而生之，子全而归之，可谓孝矣；不朽其体，不辱其身，可谓全矣</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。《孝经》有：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;&hellip;&hellip;</font><font face="宋体">身体发肤，受之父母，不敢毁伤，孝之始也</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。儒道圆融是葛洪道教思想独具一格的重要特征，儒道二家思想对葛洪的生命意识产生了重要的影响，葛洪承认自己借助并吸取了儒家伦常，一方面是出于道教修行伦理建设的需要，另一方面也有利于为道教在传统宗法伦理社会中寻找立足之地。他认为，人作为</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">七尺之形骸，禀之以所生</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，禀先天之气而生，即禀道而生。生命之于人是高贵却又十分短暂的，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">人生倏忽，以过隙之促，诧罔极之间，迅乎犹奔星之暂见，飘乎似飞矢之电经</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>22</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">在道教所构想的上至极远之玄天、下至极深之地府的宇宙之中，生命倏之即逝，忽然而已，高贵的人怎能不珍视生命呢？怎能不选择全其身却反倒去<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">归残</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">呢？</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">再次，葛洪直言不讳地提出<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">方寸之心</font><font face="Times New Roman">,&nbsp;</font><font face="宋体">制之在我</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span>23</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这种我命在我、心作主宰的思想，展示了道教对个体自我自由选择的重视，体现了道教对生命的尊严感，在葛洪看来，人应当成为自我生命的主人。尽管<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">金虽克木，而锥钻不可以伐邓林；水虽胜火，而升合不足以救焚山。寸膠不能治黄河之濁，尺水不能却萧丘之热</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>24</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一人的力量微不足道，却可以控制自己的生命，做出自己的人生选择，把握好命运，不同流，不合污，<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">养浩然于幽人之仵</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，出离于政治之外，保全自我真性不受俗流污染，与隐幽高洁之人为伍，培育正而无邪的畅然之气，就是对生命的最好把控，是对生命真正的尊重。如果不能很好地把握生命，就等于是</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">复举熠耀以厕日月之间，拊甂瓴于洪锺之侧，贡轻扇于坚冰之节，炫裘炉乎隆暑之月</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>25</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">不仅如秋扇见捐而无用，还会遭人嗤笑，有小狐湿尾之嫌。历史上的要离、纪信、陈贾、仲由之流，不过是<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">下愚</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">而非</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">上智</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">之人。他还认真分析了这样选择的价值所在：既能</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">全真成名</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，养其志以全真性，又能弘道养正，弥补儒家教化之不足。卑微之人在某一个方面加以保全，不苛求完满就应当知足了，这反映了道教吸收儒家思想后对入仕的认识和选择。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">葛洪的<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">弘道养正</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，即是说要发扬光大</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">道</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，以培育正气。因为</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">道存则尊，德胜则贵</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，只有</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">高尚其志</font><font face="Times New Roman">,&nbsp;</font><font face="宋体">不仕王侯</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，按易辞的爻象，依天理，才能修养圣人之德。《论语</font><font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font><font face="宋体">卫灵公十五》的</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">人能弘道，非道弘人</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，是儒家的弘道态度。然而葛洪这个</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">弘道</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">也不完全同于儒家，因为它是在吸收了杨朱</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">贵己重生</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">、</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">不以物累形</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，并在庄子保全人的精神自由思想的基础上，借鉴了儒家的伦常思想，并做了一番融儒入道的功夫，从中我们不难看出葛洪一生由儒入道思想转变的端倪，这也是他隐逸理论的一大特点，也符合其</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">殊途一致</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">之说法。对于是入仕还是隐逸、二者孰轻孰重的取与舍问题，葛洪旗帜鲜明，凸显了他超脱于尘俗之外，不受物欲诱迫，不</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">苦形于外物</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，空灵湛然的道教精神。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">三、藏光守朴，逍遥隐遁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">魏晋时代，天下纷纷扰扰，特别是统治集团间的相互倾轧，社会动荡不安，人的生命都难以保全。士大夫们的人生观发生了巨变，治平天下、建功立业的人生价值追求，为闲适恬淡、隐退山林、自由自在、求得自我所取代。尘世的喧嚣纷扰带来了恐怖与痛苦，世人绞尽脑汁以求功名，活得太累，而且随时存在着生命危险，不如啸傲山林，闲云野鹤，轻松自如，以求自保。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">葛洪也离不开他的时代和他士族身份的背景，有那个时代的烙印，鲁迅曾称赞其<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">论及晋末社会状态</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。他将隐仕怀冰先生描述为</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">秘六奇以括囊，含琳琅而不吐。谧清音则莫之或闻，掩辉藻则世不得睹</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>26</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">突出其含藏内敛的品格。葛洪明确地阐明其道教思想：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">藏光守朴；表拙示讷，知止常足</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span>27</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">藏光守朴</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，乃道教所崇尚之道的主要特征，即幽隐深邃、含藏内敛、素朴无华。《道德经》讲</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">明道若昧，进道若退</font><font face="Times New Roman">&hellip;&hellip;</font><font face="宋体">质真若渝，大白若辱</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>28</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">见素抱朴</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span>29</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">等。道教之道的显现不是外炫的，而是返照的，它幽隐含藏，不求外在的华美，一切以简示之，素朴是道的品质。<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">表拙示讷</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，取自《道德经》</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">大巧若拙，大辩若讷</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>30</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">意思是最灵巧的东西好像是笨拙的一样，最卓越的辩才像是口讷一样，仍然反映了做人不必求外形上的表露，而着力于内在生命的含藏。<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">知止常足</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">源于《道德经》第四十四章：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">知足不辱，知止不殆</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">、</font></span><span>31</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">祸莫大于不知足，咎莫大于欲得。故知足之足，常足矣</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>32</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">强调了贪得而不知足必生祸患。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">葛洪十分欣赏<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">咀嚼芝芳，风飞云浮；晞景九阳，附翼高游；仰栖梧桐，俯集玄洲</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span>33</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这样的逍遥生活，他设想<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">寝宜僚之舍</font><font face="Times New Roman">,&nbsp;</font><font face="宋体">闭干木之闾</font><font face="Times New Roman">,&nbsp;</font><font face="宋体">携庄莱之友</font><font face="Times New Roman">,&nbsp;</font><font face="宋体">治陋巷之居</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">侣云鹏以高逝</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>34</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">同庄子、老莱子这样的高尚隐士携游，<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">优游以自得</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。他所说的</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">逍遥竹素，寄情玄毫</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>35</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">正是逍遥自在、博览古籍、潜心著述、避世隐居的道人情趣。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">葛洪征引了《庄子<font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font><font face="宋体">列御寇》中的一个典故，祭祀的牛披着纹彩锦繍，饲着刍草大豆，等到一朝被牵到太庙成为牺牲时，牛的生命就会被釿没。葛洪讲庄子不仕、崇尚隐逸，是想表明自己的隐逸思想。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">在《嘉遁》中，赴势公子的追问极有代表性：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">如果人人都像许由洗耳不受，耦耕本分，那谁来治国理政呢？</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">怀冰先生的回答就很有个性，他自谦地说：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">我虽不善治国理政，然而有满朝文武，还用担心众多的事务治理不好吗？</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">我扬长避短，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">若拥经著述，可以全真成名，有补末化</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">切磋后生，弘道养正</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>36</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这样一来可能没有了<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">立朝之勋，即戎之劳</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，可是最终是殊途一致的。李刚先生曾讲：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">葛洪要实现其理想的生命追求，儒道互补，仙圣双修，就必须对儒道关系作出合理的解释，这才能令人信服</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span>37</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">葛洪就是在道与儒的选择中体现出了他的调解之意，所以他并不是绝对的隐而无所作为，也不是致力于有为而不知时适的进退。他出身于封建社会内部的高级士族家庭，从小博览百家之书，<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">以儒学知名</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。但社会的动荡，家道的没落，使其立功无望，于是，自认</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">才非政事，器乏治民</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，从而转向</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">不仕为荣</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">的</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">立言</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">方面，他要</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">拥经著述</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">立言助教</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>38</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">兴儒教以救微言之绝</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span>39</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">他把教化风俗、立言有为、当隐则隐、当行则行与清静寡欲、不仕政事、高韬隐遁、保全真性融合起来，道本儒末，儒道圆融，不能不承认葛洪给予了本篇命题以十分准确的定位。那位赴势公子的话为葛洪独特的道教思想作了恰到好处的注解：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">无所必固。时止则止，时行则行</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span>40</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">即恰到好处的隐遁，待机而动。文中葛洪<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">明哲保身</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">的提法，其实是想说明智之人无论出世还是隐遁，都是要以全身保真为前提的，对此我们不能简单地将其归结为士族出身或爵禄无望所致，而看不到葛洪儒道圆融的大智慧，看不到一位真正的道教思想者救世之鸿志。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">注：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">①②③④⑤⑥⑦⑧⑨⑩</span><span>11</span><span>12</span><span>13</span><span>16</span><span>17</span><span>18</span><span>19</span><span>21</span><span>22</span><span>23</span><span>24</span><span>25</span><span>26</span><span>27</span><span>33</span><span>34</span><span>35</span><span>36</span><span>38</span><span>39</span><span>40</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">杨明照：《抱朴子<font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font><font face="宋体">外篇校笺》（上），中华书局，</font><font face="Times New Roman">1991</font><font face="宋体">年</font><font face="Times New Roman">12</font><font face="宋体">月版，前言第</font><font face="Times New Roman">1</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">2</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">1</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">23</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">16</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">32</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">23</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">32</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">47</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">23</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">47</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">42</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">32</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">44</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">42</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">44</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">44</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">27</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">44</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">42</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">59</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">1</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">47</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">47</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">23</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">44</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">59</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">61</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">61</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">52</font><font face="宋体">页。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑤</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">陈鼓应：《庄子今注今译》（中）《知北游》，中华书局，<font face="Times New Roman">2009</font><font face="宋体">年</font><font face="Times New Roman">2</font><font face="宋体">月版，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">601</font><font face="宋体">页。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>14</span><span>15</span><span>20</span><span>28</span><span>29</span><span>30</span><span>31</span><span>32</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">陈鼓应：《老子注译及评介》，中华书局，<font face="Times New Roman">1984</font><font face="宋体">年</font><font face="Times New Roman">5</font><font face="宋体">月版，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">136</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">244</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">124</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">227</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">136</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">241</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">239</font><font face="宋体">页，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">244</font><font face="宋体">页。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>37</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">李刚：《何以<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">中国根柢全在道教</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">》，四川出版集团巴蜀书社，</font><font face="Times New Roman">2008</font><font face="宋体">年</font><font face="Times New Roman">11</font><font face="宋体">月版，第</font><font face="Times New Roman">137</font><font face="宋体">页。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（作者分别系郧阳师范高等专科学校政法与旅游系教授，武汉大学哲学学院本科生）</span></p>
